cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >
  If you use this software, please cite the primary methodology paper
  (preferred-citation below). For specific features, also cite the
  feature-specific paper from the references list: ACS Nano 2022 for
  strain extraction, and Phys. Rev. X 2023 for multi-layered calculations.
title: "moire_metrology"
abstract: >
  A Python package for moire relaxation, strain extraction, and multi-layer
  analysis of two-dimensional moire superlattices.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Halbertal
    given-names: Dorri
version: 0.7.1
date-released: 2026-04-13
license: MIT
doi: "10.5281/zenodo.19468557"
identifiers:
