    value: "10.5281/zenodo.19468557"
    description: "Zenodo concept DOI — always resolves to the latest released version of the software."
  - type: doi
    value: "10.5281/zenodo.19468558"
    description: "Zenodo version DOI for v0.1.0."
repository-code: "https://github.com/dorrih/moire_metrology"
url: "https://github.com/dorrih/moire_metrology"
keywords:
  - moire
  - 2D materials
  - lattice relaxation
  - strain extraction
  - van der Waals heterostructures
  - condensed matter physics

